text: Darmstadt is a city in Germany, in the state of Hesse. It has about 140,000 inhabitants and a university. The chemical element named darmstadtium is named after the city. == References == == Other websites == * Official site of the city of Darmstadt (German, English) * Darmstadt on Wikivoyage * Mathildenhoehe * Details of Trams and Buses used in Darmstadt * Public Transport in Darmstadt - Maps, Timetables, Fares * War memorials in Darmstadt
